<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id5a493063-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c" identifier="/us/usc/t29/s465"><num value="465">§ 465.</num><heading> Report to Congress</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall submit to the Congress at the expiration of three years from <date date="1959-09-14">September 14, 1959</date>, a report upon the operation of this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id5a493064-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c">(<ref href="/us/pl/86/257/tIII/s305">Pub. L. 86–257, title III, § 305</ref>, <date date="1959-09-14">Sept. 14, 1959</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/73/532">73 Stat. 532</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
